claim.claim-text:
1. A lighting module comprising:
a light guide plate;
a first case coupled to one side of the light guide plate;
a first light source which is disposed in the first case and emits light to the one side of the light guide plate;
a second case coupled to the other side of the light guide plate; and
a second light source which is disposed in the second case and emits light to the other side of the light guide plate
wherein an amount of light which is emitted through a top surface of the light guide plate is equal to or not equal to an amount of light which is emitted through a bottom surface of the light guide plate,
wherein the first case comprises a base in which the first light source is disposed, a first extension part extending from the base and a second extension part extending from the base, and
wherein a length of the first extension part is less than a length of the second extension part.

12. A lighting module of comprising:
a light guide plate;
a first case coupled to one side of the light guide plate;
a light source which is disposed in the first case and emits light to the one side of the light guide plate;
a second case coupled to the other side of the light guide plate; and
a second light source which is disposed in the second case and emits light to the other side of the light guide plate
wherein an amount of light which is emitted through a top surface of the light guide plate is equal to or not equal to an amount of light which is emitted through a bottom surface of the light guide plate,
wherein the light guide plate comprises a first light guide plate including a first inclined surface and comprises a second light guide plate including a second inclined surface disposed to face the first inclined surface, and further comprising a reflective plate disposed between the first inclined surface and the second inclined surface,
wherein the reflective plate comprises a top surface and a bottom surface and wherein the top and the bottom surfaces of the reflective plate are coated with reflective materials having mutually different reflectances respectively.

14. A lighting module comprising:
a first light guide plate;
a second light guide plate disposed below the first light guide plate;
a reflective plate between the first light guide plate and the second light guide plate;
a first and a second light sources which are disposed on both sides of the first light guide plate respectively;
a third and a fourth light sources which are disposed on both sides of the second light guide plate respectively;
a first case coupled to one side of the first light guide plate and to one side of the second light guide plate; and
a second case coupled to the other side of the first light guide plate and to the other side of the second light guide plate,
wherein the reflective plate comprises a micro lens.
